            "kicker": "",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h5>LOCAL DELIVERY</h5><p>Orders within South Africa are delivered within 2–3 business days.</p><h5>INTERNATIONAL DELIVERY</h5><p>Due to current global conditions, international orders may take 2–3 weeks to arrive. Your matcha is sealed and packaged to remain completely fresh throughout the journey- it will be worth the wait.</p><p>Please note that international orders may be subject to customs duties, tariffs, or import fees upon arrival. These are the responsibility of the recipient. For any questions about applicable fees, we recommend contacting your local post office or delivery provider directly.</p>",
