        "text_xPAVxU": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "kicker": "",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h5>PROTECTED WITH EVERY ORDER</h5><p>We've partnered with ITUNL to protect your order against loss, damage, or theft because once it leaves our hands, we still want it to reach yours. If your package is lost or arrives damaged, filing a claim is simple and straightforward. For packages marked as delivered but not received, claims must be filed between 5 and 15 days from the marked delivery date. For packages not marked as delivered, claims can be filed after 7 days from the last tracking checkpoint (20 days for international orders), and within 30 days of that checkpoint.</p><p>Any questions? Reach us at <a href=\"mailto:accounts@ceremonymatchabar.com\" title=\"mailto:accounts@ceremonymatchabar.com\">accounts@ceremonymatchabar.com</a> and we will take care of you.<br/><br/></p>",
