          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "kicker": "",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>At Ceremony, quality is not just a promise — it is our standard. If something is ever not right, we want to hear from you.</p><h5>OUR COMMITMENT</h5><p>We do not offer cash refunds. Where eligible, store credit will be issued so you can find something that truly works for you.</p><h5>MATCHA + TEAWARE</h5><p>Out of care for your safety and ours, we are unable to accept returns on any matcha-related goods, this includes The Matcha, The Chasen and The Chawan. As consumable and ceremonial goods, returns are not something we are able to accommodate at this time. That said, if your matcha does not meet your expectations in any way, please contact us immediately. We will make it right - no hesitation, guaranteed.</p>",
