            "title": "",
            "text": "<h5>Merchandise</h5><p>For all other merchandise, returns are accepted within 7 days of receipt, provided the item is unused, in its original condition and with all labels intact. Items showing signs of wear or with labels removed will not be accepted for return or exchange. Please note that shipping fees are non-refundable. Any store credit or refund issued will reflect the product cost only.</p><h5>How to Start a Return</h5><p>Reach out to us before sending anything back and we will guide you through the process from there. We are here to make this as smooth as possible.</p>",
